  (201, 'Arcanist Regalia', 'misc', 'Mage', 'Tier 1', 'Tier 1 came from the fiery heart of Molten Core, WoW\'s first true 40-man raid. These lava-forged epics embodied the essence of raiding: helm and shoulders dropping from bosses like Garr and Golemagg, and the final legs claimed from Ragnaros himself. Attunement to Molten Core required braving Blackrock Depths, further cementing Tier 1 as the gateway to endgame raiding. The sets cemented raid identity, with class-defining looks like the Warrior\'s Might and the Mage\'s Arcanist Regalia. <span class=\'set-note\'>(Classic launch, Phase 1)</span>', 8, 'T1', 250, 1),
