  (241, 'Shard of the Gods', 'world', 'Druid', 'Shard of the Gods', 'A caster-oriented set of trinkets from Molten Core. Highly prized by <b>Mages</b>, <b>Warlocks</b>, <b>Priests</b>, and other casters for its unique spellpower bonuses. Owning both was a sign of serious raiding commitment.', 2, 'WD_Shard', 1440, 1),
