  (261, 'Spirit of Eskhandar', 'world', 'Druid', 'Spirit of Eskhandar', 'A rare four-piece set from Zul\'Gurub and world bosses. It combined <b>Eskhandar\'s Right Claw</b>, <b>Eskhandar\'s Left Claw</b>, <b>Eskhandar\'s Collar</b>, and <b>Eskhandar\'s Pelt</b>. Favored by <b>Warriors</b>, <b>Rogues</b>, <b>Hunters</b>, and <b>Shamans</b> for its feral-inspired bonuses.', 4, 'WD_Eskhandar', 1810, 1),
