  (384, 'Field Marshal\'s Battlegear', 'pvp', 'Warrior', 'Rank 13 - Field Marshal / Warlord', 'The apex of PvP armor progression. Unlocks <b>epic helm, chest, and shoulders</b>, completing the 6-piece epic PvP set. These were endgame BiS for battleground and world PvP players, and a symbol of incredible time investment.', 3, 'PvP_R13', 1820, 1),
