  (41, 'Dal\'Rend\'s Arms', 'world', 'Death Knight', 'Dal\'Rend\'s Arms', 'A dual-wield sword set dropped in Upper Blackrock Spire. Widely considered a pre-raid BiS choice for <b>Fury Warriors</b> and <b>Rogues</b> thanks to its high attack power bonus and accessibility before raids.', 2, 'WD_DalRend', 1350, 1),
