  (461, 'The Twin Blades of Hakkari', 'world', 'Death Knight', 'The Twin Blades of Hakkari', 'Iconic weapons from Zul\'Gurub, these twin swords symbolized the power of the Gurubashi trolls. Popular with <b>Rogues</b> and <b>Warriors</b>, they offered solid stats and thematic flair.', 2, 'WD_Hakkari', 1490, 1),
