  (463, 'Primal Blessing', 'world', 'Death Knight', 'Primal Blessing', 'A Zul\'Gurub set that granted a chance to transform into a tiger on hit, boosting attack power. Loved by <b>Rogues</b>, <b>Hunters</b>, and <b>Feral Druids</b> for its style and strength.', 2, 'WD_Primal', 1550, 1),
