  (464, 'Overlord\'s Resolution', 'world', 'Death Knight', 'Overlord\'s Resolution', 'A tank-oriented world set, rarely completed, granting bonuses to survivability. Favored by <b>Warriors</b> and <b>Paladins</b> who specialized in mitigation.', 2, 'WD_Overlord', 1650, 1),
