  (465, 'Prayer of the Primal', 'world', 'Druid', 'Prayer of the Primal', 'A Zul\'Gurub set aimed at healers. Provided mana efficiency and throughput boosts for <b>Priests</b>, <b>Paladins</b>, <b>Shamans</b>, and <b>Druids</b> in early raid healing.', 2, 'WD_Prayer', 1690, 1),
