  (466, 'Major Mojo Infusion', 'world', 'Death Knight', 'Major Mojo Infusion', 'A quirky trinket-based set from Zul\'Gurub granting spell crit and utility. While not core progression gear, it was a fun and flavorful bonus for both casters and hybrids.', 2, 'WD_Mojo', 1760, 1),
