  (474, 'Vindicator\'s Battlegear', 'misc', 'Warrior', 'Tier 1.5', 'Zul\'Gurub introduced a 20-man raid experience distinct from Molten Core. Instead of full 8-piece sets, Tier 1.5 delivered 5-piece collections, offering 2, 3, and 5-piece bonuses. These jungle-themed armor sets tied into the Zandalar Troll empire and required reputation with the Zandalar Tribe. They gave mid-tier guilds a unique progression path and provided catch-up gear for raiders not yet ready for Blackwing Lair. <span class=\'set-note\'>(Patch 1.7 "Rise of the Blood God")</span>', 5, 'T1_5', 280, 1),
  (475, 'Freethinker\'s Armor', 'misc', 'Paladin', 'Tier 1.5', 'Zul\'Gurub introduced a 20-man raid experience distinct from Molten Core. Instead of full 8-piece sets, Tier 1.5 delivered 5-piece collections, offering 2, 3, and 5-piece bonuses. These jungle-themed armor sets tied into the Zandalar Troll empire and required reputation with the Zandalar Tribe. They gave mid-tier guilds a unique progression path and provided catch-up gear for raiders not yet ready for Blackwing Lair. <span class=\'set-note\'>(Patch 1.7 "Rise of the Blood God")</span>', 5, 'T1_5', 290, 1),
